org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.bridge.VeluxBridge

  • Packages that use VeluxBridge 
    Package Description
    org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.bridge
    Classes for Generic protocol-independent interactions to IO-homecontrolled devices via the Velux gateway.
    org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.bridge.json
    JSON-protocol specific implementations of the interactions to IO-homecontrolled devices.
    org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.bridge.slip
    SLIP-protocol specific implementations of the interactions to IO-homecontrolled devices.
    org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.handler
    Classes for handling any kind of openHAB events and requests, providing a synchronisation between openHAB and the real world.
